To cite teili in publications, please use:

 M. Milde, A. Renner, K. Burelo, S. Solinas, N. Risi, M. Rasetto, V. Leite, A. M. Whatley. teili: A toolbox for building and testing neural algorithms and computational primitives using spiking neurons. Unreleased software, Institute of Neuroinformatics, University of Zurich and ETH Zurich, 2018.

A BibTeX entry for LaTeX users is

@misc{teili,
author		= {Moritz Milde and Alpha Renner and Karla Burelo and Sergio Solinas and Nicoletta Risi and Marco Rasetto and Vanessa Leite and Adrian M. Whatley},
title		= {teili: A toolbox for building and testing neural algorithms and computational primitives using spiking neurons},
year		= {2018},
note		= {Unreleased software, Institute of Neuroinformatics, University of Zurich and ETH Zurich}
}

